    rdfs:comment "The source is very close to Man in meaning, but it is not fixed to a single explicit basis across the compared definitions. Man is the relevant comparison target, but exact equivalence was rejected because the source can cover sex, cultural gender role, or both. Created with support from the Mapping Assistant."@en,
        "The source value Male is defined with person wording while also being used as a selectable coded value. Man is the relevant target because it captures persons classified as male, but exact equivalence was rejected because the source still collapses sex and gender and does not commit cleanly to a person class. Created with support from the Mapping Assistant."@en ;
    owl:annotatedProperty hriv:hasExactMeaning ;
